<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Colecciones — Quiéreme</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Allura&family=Syne:wght@600;700;800&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="ether" id="ether"></div>

<nav>
  <div class="logo">Quiéreme</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="index.html">Inicio</a></li>
    <li><a href="collections.html" class="active">Colecciones</a></li>
    <li><a href="about.html">Nuestra Historia</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button id="cart-toggle">Bag (<span id="cart-count">0</span>)</button>
</nav>

<header class="page-header">
  <h1>Catorce Fragancias</h1>
  <p>Every scent tells its own story — first spray, the wear, the linger.</p>
</header>

<div class="filters">
  <button class="filter-btn active" data-collection="all">All Scents</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-collection="night">The Night Collection</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-collection="floral">Luxury Floral</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-collection="earthy">Atmospheric &amp; Earthy</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-collection="cozy">Cozy &amp; Nostalgic</button>
</div>

<section class="grid-section">
  <div class="grid" id="product-grid"></div>
</section>

<section class="constellation reveal">
  <h2>Real stories, real obsessions</h2>
  <p class="sub">Hover a light to read what someone felt wearing it — replace with real reviews once you have them</p>
  <div class="sphere-field" id="sphere-field"></div>
</section>

<section class="discovery reveal">
  <h2>Build your Discovery Palette</h2>
  <p>With fourteen scents, you shouldn't have to choose blind. Pick 3 to 5 samples to build your own set.</p>
  <div class="discovery-counter"><span id="discovery-count">0</span> of 5 samples selected</div>
  <div class="discovery-chips" id="discovery-chips"></div>
  <button class="discovery-cta" id="add-discovery-set">Add Discovery Set to Bag</button>
</section>

<section class="quiz-launcher reveal">
  <h2>Not sure where to start?</h2>
  <p>Take the 3-question Scent Finder and we'll match you to your fragrance.</p>
  <button id="open-quiz">Find My Scent</button>
</section>

<div class="modal-overlay" id="quiz-modal">
  <div class="modal">
    <button class="modal-close" id="close-quiz">&times;</button>
    <div id="quiz-body"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>Quiéreme &mdash; una obsesión hermosa &mdash; four collections, fourteen stories</footer>

<div class="cart-drawer" id="cart-drawer">
  <button class="cart-drawer-close" id="close-cart">&times;</button>
  <h3>Your Bag</h3>
  <div id="cart-items"></div>
</div>

<script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>